name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On July 24, the Xi'an Education Bureau released a plan to deal with the "returning students" incident in the high school entrance examination.
1. The original enrollment plan will be used entirely for candidates in this city, excluding the 3,608 "returning students" previously counted.
2. These 3,608 "returning students" will continue to be admitted according to their scores and preferences, and will not occupy the original enrollment quota.
3. For those who commit fraud and violations, the admission qualification of the candidates will be revoked.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
It should be noted that the core demand of parents is that there are far more than 3,608 "returning students". However, the notice still insists on the conclusion that there are only 3,608 "returning students".
However, combined with the previous announcement by Xi'an Public Security Bureau that a number of fake educational institutions that forged government seals were seized, it is possible that only 3,608 qualified returnees were identified, and the rest of the Henan candidates were all disqualified for fraud and other illegal and irregular behaviors.
